title: in Berlin, after 2 AM 🕵🏻 [Full video, Sunday 9 am]
Berlin after Midnight?
description:
I've been living in Germany for a while now. Recently, I had to make an early morning flight, which required me to leave my house in the middle of the night. I captured my entire journey from home to the airport in a video, which I'm happy to share. #MountainTrekker #Germany #TravelVlog
